      "text": "History\n- 1991: project start\n         James Gosling, Mike Sheridan, and Patrick Naughton\n- 1996: version 1.O\n         write once, run anywhere (WORA)\n- 1997: version 1.1\n- 1998: Java Community Process (JCP) \n          Java Specification Request (JSR)\n- 1998: version 1.2\n- 2000: version 1.3\n- 2002: version 1.4\n- 2004: version 5 (1.5)\n- 2006: version 6 (1.6)\n- 2011: version 7 (1.7)\n- 2014: version 8 (1.8) LTS\n- 2017-18: version 9, 10\n- 2018: version 11 LTS\n- 2019-21: version 12, 13, 14, 15, 16\n- 2021: version 17 LTS\n- 2022-23: version 18, 19, 20\n- 2023: version 21 LTS\n- 2024-25: version 22, 23, 24\n- 2025: version 25 LTS\n- 2026: version 26, 27\n",
      "fontSize": 36,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "History\n- 1991: project start\n         James Gosling, Mike Sheridan, and Patrick Naughton\n- 1996: version 1.O\n         write once, run anywhere (WORA)\n- 1997: version 1.1\n- 1998: Java Community Process (JCP) \n          Java Specification Request (JSR)\n- 1998: version 1.2\n- 2000: version 1.3\n- 2002: version 1.4\n- 2004: version 5 (1.5)\n- 2006: version 6 (1.6)\n- 2011: version 7 (1.7)\n- 2014: version 8 (1.8) LTS\n- 2017-18: version 9, 10\n- 2018: version 11 LTS\n- 2019-21: version 12, 13, 14, 15, 16\n- 2021: version 17 LTS\n- 2022-23: version 18, 19, 20\n- 2023: version 21 LTS\n- 2024-25: version 22, 23, 24\n- 2025: version 25 LTS\n- 2026: version 26, 27\n",
