      "text": "Primitifs (8)\n\n    byte                     Byte\n    char                     Character\n    boolean                 Boolean\n    short                    Short\n    int                       Integer\n    long                     Long\n    float                    Float\n    double                  Double\n\nObjects\n\n    BigDecimal, BigInteger\n    String\n    enum (Java 5)\n    \n    Date (Java 1.0) , Calendar (Java 1.1) \n    vs \n    LocalDate, LocalTime, LocalDateTime, ZonedDateTime (Java 8)\n    ",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Primitifs (8)\n\n    byte                     Byte\n    char                     Character\n    boolean                 Boolean\n    short                    Short\n    int                       Integer\n    long                     Long\n    float                    Float\n    double                  Double\n\nObjects\n\n    BigDecimal, BigInteger\n    String\n    enum (Java 5)\n    \n    Date (Java 1.0) , Calendar (Java 1.1) \n    vs \n    LocalDate, LocalTime, LocalDateTime, ZonedDateTime (Java 8)\n    ",
